  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study investigates the beneficial effects of prefrontal brain stimulation (with
      transcranial direct current stimulation [tDCS]) during working memory training in seniors
      with mild cognitive impairments.The placebo-controlled double blinded study includes 50
      elderly patients which will be randomized into verum or sham tDCS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
